data.description: Cute Cottage style home in a great location that is just minutes to downtown Covington!  Open living area with high ceilings connects to kitchen and dining.  Cozy front porch to sit and enjoy an afternoon breeze.  This 3 bedroom, 2 full bath includes a concrete drive and parking pad, fenced-in rear yard that backs up to a greenspace, and a huge bonus side porch that is great for entertaining that connects to kitchen.
